name: Merlin Bird ID
description: Merlin Bird ID is a bird identification app.

name: Uranus
description: The seventh, third-farthest, coldest, most askew, and most unfortunately-named planet in the Solar System. This particular depiction comes from Balatro, where Uranus can help level up the Two Pair hand for you.

name: Heavenly cookies
description: Heavenly cookies is one of the first Heavenly Upgrades in Cookie Clicker.

name: BLÅHAJ
description: A plush shark sold at IKEA stores. It's achieved a rather impressive popularity considering its origins, particularly within the trans community, as it shares colors with the trans flag.

name: Elemental Man (top)
description: The top half of the element "Elemental", as seen in the alchemy-like game "Elemental Zero". The left side represents fire, the right side, air.

name: EoD invite
description: A QR code to the Elemental on Discord server.

name: Weegee
description: The Green Thunder himself, Luigi, as depicted in the DOS version of his first starring role, Mario Is Missing! His... uncanny appearance here has inspired memes since 2007.

name: International Symbol of Access
description: The presence of this sign indicates that the area the sign is in is wheelchair-accessible. At least, in theory.

name: Elemer Skip
description: A rather infamous element, known for killing the tree sizes of several other elements. Some of its victims stood mighty and tall before their deaths, while others were killed just for the memes.

name: Upvote emoji
description: The "up_arrow" emoji on Discord. Elemental on Discord uses this for polls; 3 more of these than downvotes will make a poll pass.

name: Downvote emoji
description: The "down_arrow" emoji on Discord. Elemental on Discord uses this for polls; 3 more of these than upvotes will make a poll decline.

name: Updownvote emoji
description: The "up_down_arrow" emoji on Discord. Elemental on Discord doesn't usually use these for polls, but the userbase informally uses them as an indicator for being on the fence of a poll.

name: Emblazon
description: Sable, a mullet of 4 gyronny or and yellow-ochre fimbriated argent

name: Jimbo
description: Real name Gary McCready, he is the mascot of the game Balatro, and the face of the basic Joker card. It is in that form that he gives +4 Mult with no stipulation or requirement, a rarity in Balatro.

name: Canio
description: One of Balatro's 5 Legendary Jokers. Canio multiplies Mult by the amount of times a face card has been destroyed in his presence.

name: Chicot
description: One of Balatro's 5 Legendary Jokers. Chicot stops Boss Blinds dead in their tracks, preventing their abilities from triggering.

name: lK7c
description: lK7c is the yin-yang-like character in the top left, from a series of animations on Pixilart of the same name. Here the character is in a heavily Minecraft-inspired world.

name: Pneumonoultramicroscopicsilicovolcanoconiosis
description: A word coined in 1935 to be the longest in the English language.

name: Perkeo
description: One of Balatro's 5 Legendary Jokers. Perkeo rewards his player by creating a Negative version of a held consumable when exiting the Shop.

name: Palette
description: A palette of all 64 colors on Wplace, including the "transparent" color.

name: Fucking
description: Fucking (now Fugging) is an Austrian village whose signs were often stolen due to its name.

name: Rapid Eyes
description: A YouTube unfiction series about a game on the protagonist's computer.

name: Sylveon
description: Sylveon is a Fairy-type Pokémon originating in Pokémon X/Y, and an evolution from Eevee.

name: Trans H
description: An isometric cube structure of a capital "H", in the colors of the transgender flag.

name: Paradox Tarot
description: A Penrose triangle as a Balatro tarot card.

name: Elemental Man (bottom)
description: The bottom half of the element "Elemental", as seen in the alchemy-like game "Elemental Zero". The left side represents earth, the right side, water.

name: Baba
description: Baba is the protagonist of the game Baba is You.

name: R74n
description: A website we used to be aligned with. Then we got into a fight with its creator, both sides cut almost all contact with each other, it was a whole thing.

name: Crown
description: Crown is an aroace character from the object show Love of the S*n.

name: Captain Viridian
description: Captain Viridian is the protagonist of the game VVVVVV.

name: Gender Change Potion
description: The Gender Change Potion is a potion in Terraria that can change the player's gender.

name: Annoying Dog
description: The Annoying Dog is a gag character in UNDERTALE and DELTARUNE, often used by Toby Fox to represent himself.

name: Monster Energy
description: The "M + Claw Marks" logo of the Monster Energy drinks.

name: Redstone Torch
description: Originating from Minecraft, this item constantly creates a 100% redstone signal to (almost) all the blocks around it. It also lights rooms up a little, if you're into that.

name: Hardcore Heart
description: If you see this in your health bar while playing Minecraft, you're playing Hardcore mode. Don't die, because respawns are not allowed!
